<div class="quotetitle">Dwedit wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent"><br />I still don't understand why the FM2 format is so weird.<br /></div><br />It was a design decision that the movie file format [of FCEUX] should be easily editable with a regular editor, without need for hex editing. Needs for copypasting and trimming arise every so often.<br /><br />EDIT: nesmock now supports also fm2.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=5043">Bisqwit</a> — Mon Jan 09, 2012 11:57 pm</p><hr />
